title: Big Lips
description:
This collection was originally seeded some time in 2011. It was uploaded as an ISO file. If you downloaded it, you would find that you could only access the images by running a setup program. This would install an image manager program (Fastone) before unpacking the images, which was annoying enough. However, the setup program only worked under Win7+, which made it inaccessible to anybody running XP/Mac/Linux/etc.

I've extracted the image files and compressed them into a single RAR file unchanged.

tldr; Good collection, now more accessible. File sizes are mostly med-to-high res.
